---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Buyun Wang">
  <Navigation />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-8 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
          I'm a developer passionate about creating elegant solutions to complex problems. 
          With a focus on web technologies and user experience, I build applications that are 
          both powerful and delightful to use.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4">Experience</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          I bring extensive experience in end-to-end product delivery, spanning the entire product lifecycle from initial concept to market success. My expertise covers UI/UX design, product design, development, and data analysis, allowing me to understand and contribute to every stage of the product development process.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Over the years, I've worked with various technologies and frameworks, including 
          React, TypeScript, Node.js, and Python. This comprehensive background enables me to bridge the gap between design and development, ensuring seamless execution from ideation to deployment while leveraging data insights to drive product decisions.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4">Approach</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          I believe in writing clean, maintainable code that others can understand and build upon. 
          Every project is an opportunity to learn something new and push the boundaries of what's possible.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-4">Let's Connect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          I'm always interested in new challenges and collaborations. Whether you have a project 
          in mind or just want to chat about technology, feel free to reach out.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-8">
          <a 
            href="mailto:buyunwang@outlook.com"
            class="px-6 py-3 bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
          >
            Get in Touch
          </a>
          <a 
            href="/resume.pdf" 
            class="px-6 py-3 border border-gray-900 text-gray-900 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
          >
            Download Resume
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
